            "text_size": "30,15",
            "txt_align": "start",
            "sub_heading": "",
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h4><strong>Popular Searches<br/></strong></h4><p></p><p><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/ng-earsafe-openbuds-with-air-conduction-technology\">Ear Safe Earbuds</a> | <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/pages/bone-conduction-headphones\">Bone Conduction Headphones</a> | <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/pages/air-conduction-headphones\">Air Conduction Headphones</a> | <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/ng-earsafe-pro-open-ear-bone-conduction-headphones\">Best Swimming Headphones</a> | <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/pages/wholesale-bluetooth-headphones\">Wholesale Headphones</a> | <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/pages/open-ear-headphones-product-comparison\">Open Ear Headphones Product Comparison</a><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/ng-earsafe-pro-open-ear-bone-conduction-headphones\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/ng-earsafe-pro-open-ear-bone-conduction-headphones\"><br/></a></p><h4><br/>Top Blog Search<strong><br/></strong></h4><p></p><p><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/5-major-benefits-of-cycling\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/5-major-benefits-of-cycling\">5 major Benefits of Cycling</a>‎ ‎ |‎ ‎ <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/hearing-loss\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/hearing-loss\">Hearing Loss</a>‎ ‎ |‎ ‎ <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/why-should-you-use-open-ear-headphones\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/why-should-you-use-open-ear-headphones\">Why should you use Open-Ear Headphones?</a>‎ ‎ |‎ ‎ <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/difference-between-air-conduction-and-bone-conduction-technology\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/difference-between-air-conduction-and-bone-conduction-technology\">Difference between Air conduction and Bone Conduction</a>‎ ‎ |‎ ‎ ‎<a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/ng-earsafe-vs-ng-earsafe-comm\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/ng-earsafe-vs-ng-earsafe-comm\">NG EarSafe vs NG EarSafe Comm</a>‎ ‎ |‎ ‎ <a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/ear-infection\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/ear-infection\">Ear Infections</a>‎ ‎ |‎ ‎ ‎<a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/what-is-active-noise-cancellation\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/what-is-active-noise-cancellation\">What is Anc</a>‎ ‎ |‎ ‎ ‎<a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/open-ear-vs-in-ear-vs-over-ear-headphones\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/blogs/open-ear-headphones/open-ear-vs-in-ear-vs-over-ear-headphones\">Open-Ear vs. In-Ear vs. Over-Ear Headphones</a><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/collections/open-ear-headphones\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ngearsafe.com/collections/open-ear-headphones\"><br/><br/></a></p>",
