    "custom_html_TWXTQH": {
      "type": "custom-html",
      "settings": {
        "code": "<div class=\"t4s-text-center\" style=\"padding: 15px 0;color: #fff;\">\n    <div class=\"footer-seo\">\n        <h2>NG EarPlugs: The Ultimate Reusable Ear Plugs for Sleeping, Concerts, Travel &amp; More</h2>\n\n        <p>\n            If you’ve ever struggled to fall asleep next to a snoring partner, felt drained after a loud concert, or wished for peace while stuck in traffic, you’re not alone. The world’s noise can be overwhelming — but NG EarPlugs are here to change that. Built for modern life, these reusable, noise-cancelling earplugs offer up to 25dB sound reduction while maintaining all-day comfort and versatility. Whether you're a side sleeper, a festival-goer, or someone who just craves quiet, NG EarPlugs help you take back control of your environment.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Sleep Better with Noise-Cancelling Comfort\n\nMost of us underestimate how deeply noise affects our sleep. With NG EarPlugs, you can finally experience the best sleep ear plugs designed specifically for comfort. Made from ultra-soft silicone, they’re perfect for side sleepers, light sleepers, or those dealing with snoring partners. Unlike foam plugs that get uncomfortable or fall out, these plugs are crafted for a snug, barely-there fit — even for those with small ear canals.\n\nAnd for those suffering from misophonia, tinnitus, or a general sensitivity to sound, NG EarPlugs offer just the right amount of noise reduction — enough to create calm, but not complete silence. That makes them ideal for sleeping, studying, meditating, or working from noisy environments.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Travel in Peace – On Roads or in the Air\n\nWhether you’re riding a bike, sitting in traffic, or flying across time zones, NG EarPlugs double as your travel ear plugs. They minimize engine rumble, reduce airplane noise, and block out roadside chaos. For motorcyclists, they function as motorcycle ear plugs, cutting wind noise without muting important ambient sounds.\n\nThanks to their IP68 waterproof rating, they also double up as swimming earplugs. Use them at the beach, in the pool, or in the shower without worry. For swimmers who need open-ear audio underwater, they pair perfectly with NG EarSafe Pro.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Your Concert + Festival Companion\n\nConcerts are unforgettable — but so is the ringing in your ears afterward. NG EarPlugs offer a safer concert experience by reducing sound levels without killing the vibe. With crystal-clear audio clarity and 25dB sound dampening, they protect your hearing at clubs, music festivals, and live events.\n\nUnlike traditional earplugs, NG doesn’t compromise on style or fit. They’re nearly invisible, stay put even while dancing, and come in a compact travel case for easy portability. Say goodbye to uncomfortable foam and hello to festival-ready protection.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Why NG Beats Foam and Wax\n\nCompared to disposable foam earplugs, NG EarPlugs are reusable, washable, and more environmentally friendly. They're made from hypoallergenic silicone, which makes them suitable for long-term use — whether you're sleeping every night with them or using them for ear protection while riding or at work.\n\nAnd if you're wondering about alternatives like Loop’s Dream or Experience Plus, NG offers similar comfort and protection — but with a focus on Indian needs, pricing, and availability. You don’t need to look overseas for quality anymore.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            One Plug. Endless Possibilities.\n\nBest noise cancelling earplugs for sleeping with a snorer\n\n\nReusable earplugs for concerts and festivals\n\n\nSide sleeper-approved comfort fit\n\n\nWaterproof ear plugs for swimmers and showers\n\n\nQuiet ear plugs for overstimulation and misophonia\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Use it while you’re cycling, jogging, at your desk, or even during casual evening walks. With the <strong>Call &amp; Music switch mode</strong>, Comm 2.0 adapts to your day, allowing you to shift between productivity and entertainment in an instant.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            With NG EarPlugs, your peace of mind is just a plug away. No more tossing in bed, suffering through engine noise, or leaving concerts with damaged hearing. Wherever life gets loud — NG helps you stay safe, sleep better, and live quieter.\n        </p>\n\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n    .footer-seo {color:#ddd;padding:30px;text-align:left;border-radius:8px}\n    .footer-seo h2 {color:#fff;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo h3 {color:#fff;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo p {font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}\n</style>",
